taski (Solo)</em></strong></a></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 176, 176);\"><strong><em>NOTES:</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 203, 203);\"><em>My commissions are open! And I'm feeling super motivated so if you want to get any alts","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"tUxqMTu2MbXcFMtBhzdVV.webp","creator":"grimmitto","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov","🌗 Switch"],"chats":17961,"messages":342114,"created_at":"2025-12-03T20:36:44.217450+00:00"}